  <h1 class="page-title"><span property="schema:name" class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden opcw-has-deck">
      <span class="opcw-head">Capacity Building</span><br />
    <span class="opcw-deck">Responsible Care® Workshops</span><br />
  </span>
</h1>


  </div>
<div data-drupal-messages-fallback class="hidden"></div>
<div id="block-opcw-content" class="block block-system block-system-main-block">
  
    
      
<article role="article" about="/resources/capacity-building/international-cooperation-programmes/responsible-carer-workshops" typeof="schema:WebPage" class="node node--type-page node--view-mode-full">

  
      <span property="schema:name" content="Responsible Care® Workshops" class="rdf-meta hidden"></span>


  <div class="node__content">
    
<div class="field field--name-field-body field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items">
            <div id="on-page-menu" class="on-page-menu">
        <ul class="clearfix">
                      <li>
              <a href="#section--id--6227">About</a>
            </li>
                      <li>
              <a href="#section--id--6236">What is Responsible Care ®</a>
            </li>
                      <li>
              <a href="#section--id--6242">Host an Event</a>
            </li>
                  </ul>
      </div>
              <div id="section--id--6223" class="paragraph paragraph--type--section paragraph--view-mode--default opcw-large-type opcw-full-width">
      <div class="paragraph--type--section__wrapper clearfix">
                      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
  <p><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Sharing best practices and raising awareness for the Responsible Care ® programme. </span></span></span></p>

      </div>


  
              </div>
    </div>
  
                <div id="section--id--6227" class="paragraph paragraph--type--section paragraph--view-mode--default">
      <div class="paragraph--type--section__wrapper clearfix">
                      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
  <p>The two-week programme <span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>focuses on various elements of Responsible Care®, through a series of lectures, interactive exercises, and case studies.</span></span></span></p>

<p><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Topics covered include product stewardship, environmental protection and environmental technologies, labelling of chemicals, integrated systems for chemical safety and security management, occupational medicine, health protection, and more generally</span></span></span><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span> the OPCW and Convention, dual use and ethical issues in chemistry, and sustainability of industrial production.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Case studies presented consider the implementation of Responsible Care® in the Russian Federation and internationally. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>The workshop is currently only offered to the Member States from Eastern Europe and Central Asia and is conducted in Russian.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<h3><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Objectives</span></span></span></span></span></span></h3>

<ul><li><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Wider adoption of the Responsible Care® programme in OPCW Member States, especially those which are not the ICCA members but may wish to become so.</span></span></span></li>
	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Enhancing the culture sustainability in chemical enterprises by increasing specialist knowledge of specific aspects of Responsible Care® programme related to environmental safeguarding, health protection, and chemical safety and security.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Enhance national capacities and the preparedness of chemical industries in Member States to implement Responsible Care® and adopt related best practices on the national level. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Foster wider regional and international cooperation in the field of chemical safety and security management among stakeholders, including chemical industry, academia, national authorities and associations, and ICCA and CEFIC.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

      </div>


      <aside>  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                      
        
  <p>These workshops are conducted by OPCW’s Technical Secretariat in cooperation with the International Council of Chemical Associations (ICCA) (owner of the programme).</p>

<p><strong>Information regarding the 2019 workshop is coming in due course. </strong></p>

        

                  </div>
  
  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/eligibility_20.png?itok=QjplehSU 68w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/eligibility_20.png?itok=OVWvCY4h 135w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/eligibility_20.png?itok=QjplehSU" alt="Eligibility" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
  <h4 class="field field--name-field-heading field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Eligibility</h4>

        
  <p>Environmental health and safety managers, qualified technologists, and representatives from chemical industry associations and governmental organisations from OPCW Member States.</p>

        

                  </div>
  
  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/flaticon1528102599-svg_19.png?itok=QFjY6uNs 80w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/flaticon1528102599-svg_19.png?itok=dX5qWOZu 160w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/flaticon1528102599-svg_19.png?itok=QFjY6uNs" alt="Calendar" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
  <h4 class="field field--name-field-heading field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Current Programmes</h4>

        
  <p>Find current capacity building programmes and workshops in <a href="https://www.opcw.org/calendar">OPCW’s Calendar</a>.</p>

        

                  </div>
  
</aside>
  
              </div>
    </div>
  
                <div id="section--id--7512" class="paragraph paragraph--type--section paragraph--view-mode--default opcw-background-colour">
      <div class="paragraph--type--section__wrapper clearfix">
                      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--wayfinding-grid paragraph--view-mode--default grid-columns--2">
                

  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--wayfinding-block paragraph--view-mode--default">
                              <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/icons/chemistry_4.png?itok=hvc9nWlo 84w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/icons/chemistry_4.png?itok=Dw8FKBss 168w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/icons/chemistry_4.png?itok=hvc9nWlo" alt="Chemistry" typeof="foaf:Image" />


              
              <h3>  What is Chemical Safety?
</h3>
      
      
  <p>“Chemical safety” refers to measures to prevent non-deliberate releases of toxic chemicals into the environment and to mitigate the impact if such events occur.</p>

<p>Chemical safety comprises disciplines such as occupational safety, public safety, process safety, environment safety, consumer safety and transport safety. Many of these are also dealt with by other international conventions and by several other international bodies and lead agencies.</p>

      </div>

  

  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--wayfinding-block paragraph--view-mode--default">
                              <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/icons/shield_3.png?itok=xj7z9j98 65w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/icons/shield_3.png?itok=l4tID7kk 130w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/icons/shield_3.png?itok=xj7z9j98" alt="Sheild" typeof="foaf:Image" />


              
              <h3>  What is Chemical Security?
</h3>
      
      
  <p>“Chemical security” refers to measures to prevent deliberate releases of toxic chemicals and to mitigate the impact if such events occur.</p>

<p>In a wider context, it also includes policies to prevent attempts to acquire toxic chemicals or chemical weapons precursors.</p>

      </div>


        </div>


  
              </div>
    </div>
  
                <div id="section--id--6236" class="paragraph paragraph--type--section paragraph--view-mode--default">
      <div class="paragraph--type--section__wrapper clearfix">
                      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
  <h3><span><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span>What is the Responsible Care ® Programme?</span></span></span></span></span></span></h3>

<p><span><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span>R</span></span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>esponsible Care® is the global chemical industry’s unique initiative to improve health, environmental performance, enhance security, and to communicate with stakeholders about products and processes. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Responsible Care commits companies, national chemical industry associations and their partners to:</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

      </div>


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--content-grid paragraph--view-mode--default section--id--6235">
                


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/sustainable_3.png?itok=cpj1BIF6 80w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/sustainable_3.png?itok=MFxvaOcd 160w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/sustainable_3.png?itok=cpj1BIF6" alt="Sustainable" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
        
  <p>Continuously improve the environmental, health, safety and security knowledge and performance of our technologies, processes and products over their life cycles so as to avoid harm to people and the environment.</p>

        

                  </div>
  
  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/exchange_1.png?itok=nKicqslX 80w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/exchange_1.png?itok=aMFDKBgG 160w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/exchange_1.png?itok=nKicqslX" alt="exchange" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
        
  <p>Use resources efficiently and minimise waste.</p>

        

                  </div>
  
  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/evaluation_2.png?itok=YSaO5XXQ 80w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/evaluation_2.png?itok=Q_6WIjNe 160w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/evaluation_2.png?itok=YSaO5XXQ" alt="evaluation" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
        
  <p>Report openly on performance, achievements and shortcomings.</p>

        

                  </div>
  
  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/development-exchange_2.png?itok=QXW5eVtL 80w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/development-exchange_2.png?itok=4voGFL04 160w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/development-exchange_2.png?itok=QXW5eVtL" alt="exchange" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
        
  <p>Listen, engage and work with people to understand and address their concerns and expectations.</p>

        

                  </div>
  
  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/checkmark_19.png?itok=N5AmMJ9W 104w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/checkmark_19.png?itok=-jcAj3FA 208w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/checkmark_19.png?itok=N5AmMJ9W" alt="checkmark" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
        
  <p>Cooperate with governments and organisations in the development and implementation of effective regulations and standards, and to meet or go beyond them.</p>

        

                  </div>
  
  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/team_28.png?itok=IjzKhUSv 107w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/team_28.png?itok=N5A7lVh- 213w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/team_28.png?itok=IjzKhUSv" alt="Team" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
        
  <p>Provide help and advice to foster the responsible management of chemicals by all those who manage and use them along the product chain.</p>

        

                  </div>
  

        </div>


  
              </div>
    </div>
  
                <div id="section--id--6242" class="paragraph paragraph--type--section paragraph--view-mode--default opcw-background-colour">
      <div class="paragraph--type--section__wrapper clearfix">
                      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default">
          
  <h3><span><span><span><span><span lang="EN" xml:lang="EN"><span><span>Host an Event</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h3>

<p><span><span><span><span lang="NL" xml:lang="NL"><span><span>Member States interested in hosting an event for their chemical industry or regionally should submit a detailed request to the Secretariat. The event would be organised in consultation with the hosting Member State and/​or Institution.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

      </div>


      <aside>  


      <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--sidebar-content paragraph--view-mode--default">
                                    <div class="icon">  <img srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/mountain_7.png?itok=Xq2-a2Gp 83w, /sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon_retina/public/images/sidebar/mountain_7.png?itok=7D-WOBDo 167w" sizes="100vw" src="/sites/default/files/styles/sidebar_icon/public/images/sidebar/mountain_7.png?itok=Xq2-a2Gp" alt="Mountain" typeof="foaf:Image" />

</div>
                          
  <h4 class="field field--name-field-heading field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">Impact</h4>

        
  <p>More than 1500 participants took part in these seminars from 2009 — 2018. </p>

        

                  </div>
  
</aside>
  
              </div>
    </div>
  
